      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based, <strong>hob-safe oven-proof casserole dish</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a knob of <strong>butter </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Note: Make sure your dish is oven-proof and safe to use on the hob. Don’t have one? Start cooking in a large, wide-based pan then transfer to an oven-proof dish and cover tightly with foil</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/empty-pot-1661415977305-x200.jpg",
